Client Sequence
1. connect
2. send request
3. read response (if appropriate)
4. repeat 2 and 3
4. close


SERVICE PROTOCOL:

session requests:
request:  create <id>
response: none

request:  status <id>
response: (live|dead)

request:  kill <id>
response: none

token requests:
request:  store_token <id> <token> <data>
response: none

request:  token <id> <token>
response: <data>

request: close
response: none


ADMIN PROTOCOL:

number connections:
request: num_cxn
response: <num>

shutdown:
request: shutdown
response: none


MIRROR PROTOCOL:
no mirror requests accept a response

mirror request:
request: mirror <id>

